你能够调用以下的API:
[['MarketResearch.find_reports', {'name': 'MarketResearch.find_reports', 'description': 'This function searches for market research reports based on market type and the number of reports required.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'marketType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of market, e.g., emerging, developed.'}, {'name': 'reportCount', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The number of reports to retrieve.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'reports', 'description': 'A list of up to the specified number of matching market research reports.'}]}], ['MarketResearch.analyze_economic_indicators', {'name': 'MarketResearch.analyze_economic_indicators', 'description': 'This function analyzes economic indicators for specified markets.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'indicators', 'type': 'ARRAY', 'description': 'An array of economic indicators to analyze, e.g., GDP_growth, inflation_rate.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'analysis', 'description': 'An analysis of the specified economic indicators for the market.'}]}], ['MarketResearch.get_stock_index_performance', {'name': 'MarketResearch.get_stock_index_performance', 'description': 'This function retrieves the performance of stock indices for a specified time frame.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'timeFrame', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The time frame for which to retrieve performance data, e.g., 1_year, 5_years.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'performance', 'description': 'Performance data of stock indices for the specified time frame.'}]}], ['MarketResearch.generate_investment_analysis', {'name': 'MarketResearch.generate_investment_analysis', 'description': 'This function generates an investment analysis report based on the provided data.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'analysisType', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The type of analysis to generate, e.g., investment_opportunities, risk_assessment.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'An investment analysis report based on the specified analysis type.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `MarketResearch.find_reports` 并传入 `marketType` 和 `reportCount`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "MarketResearch.find_reports",
    "args": "{'marketType': 'emerging', 'reportCount': 5}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
